reviews.review_text: First time trying out Canadian McDonald s and it is noticeably better than the American counterpart. The chicken nuggets were pretty crisp.

I always order my coffee here before work. I truly appreciate the consistency of the weekday early morning crew! Well made coffee, be it iced or hot, definitely makes a big impact on your morning. Kudos to this team! Tried other McDonald s store coffee and all have that sour after taste. This store s coffee in the morning tastes fresh.
Might be the most consistently fresh McDonalds fries and burgers in the lower mainland. Also, bunnies everywhere

One of the best location I have visited. Staff are friendly and they do routine floor and table cleaning which I dont see too often in some other McDonalds restaurants. Usually service is quite prompt but they do get a lunch rush and it can extend the wait time for quite a bit. Since its facing the airport, theres not much tall building around so this restaurant gets lots of warm sunlight. A limited amount of USB charging port is available. Wifi speed is about 14 Mbps download. Not a kids concentrated area so the freebies for kids such as drawing paper, color crayons, balloons have decent availability. Theres this manager whos energetic and I like his attitude towards work and customer service. He seems to recognize many regular customers and they like to have a short chat with him. One time I screwed up my one time use only mobile app coupon  he reached me offering help. He pulled his personal phone out and scan that coupon code for me. Thats exceptional customer service. Appreciated that.
I only stopped for a coffee and decided to go inside. I was pleased to see that on all of the tables there are plants. I never had such a good experience in any fast food restaurant.

Standard McDonalds service but the view of this place is amazing You can have a sip of coffee and may be a bite from your McDouble while watching big planes flying in and out of YVR. One of the best McDonalds in Vancouver in terms of view. If you are Avgeek, dont miss this McDonalds.

Consistent service and value. Never any surprises when I get my order Vegetarian options: On the menu. Parking: Can be a little tight when busy Kid-friendliness: Its McDonalds. What more can be said Wheelchair accessibility: Power doors and ample parking for easy access with a wheelchair
This location is my favourite-food is always fresh and workers are so friendly
My destination after weekday mass, love the view overlooking the airport an ample parking.

Staff were very friendly and food was served quick. Majority of the workers wore masks and the place was very clean! Fries are always very crispy. Customers definitely were not the nicest to the workers. I would for sure come back here!
Great atmosphere. Able to view the Vancouver international airport. Vegetarian options: There are different options of salads Kid-friendliness: Family restaurant

Amazing staff. They were so happy and cheerful. This is the best McDonalds experience Ive ever had. The two ladies were really enjoying their shift, and she was so happy when she took our order. Kudos to the staff, I wish I lived close by, so I could grab a coffee everyday and start my.mornings with these awesome people.
Haha Ive gone there enough where they could recognize me and would always wish me a good day.
Great McDonalds great stuff. Food was perfect once and while they mess up however they are getting better. I wish the one on Marine drive would learn from this place

They dont charge for cups! I stopped going to other McDonalds cuz I refuse to support the extortion of money. And McDonalds is not really cheap anymore and they have the nerve to charge for cups yet refuse let me use my own mug!
Great place to sit and watch activities at YVR.
Im American. The McDonalds in Canada taste, so good.
This is the best in Richmond. Enough parking to begin with and the entrance is easy compare to the one at blundell mall. To top it off the food and service are good too
We come here regularly and the staff are pretty friendly. Drive through is efficient and they are able to make changes on the fly as the app doesn t allow flexibility.
One of the best McDonalds Ive been to.

Quick response from cashier and nice service, however the waiting lane for drive through is extremely short that probably it only allow three vehicles to wait in line. Redesign the layout for drive through is urgent

This is the best McDonalds in Richmond. I live right next to 2 Blundell location but drive the extra few minutes to this location instead because it s MUCH better. The crew here are very kind and try their best. Never once was treated poorly by any staff here. Blundell location has some nasty people working there (after 11 pm crew) which make it a miserable place to go to.

I really like this particular location! Never had a single issue with any of my orders, food is always fast, always fresh. Staff is really nice, they play upbeat music (sometimes oldies) and this creates an overall enjoyable atmosphere.

This is one of the best McDonalds restaurants in the lower mainland if not  the best for dine-in. The food is delicious, the premises are always clean, the staff is extremely kind and professional and the other customers respectful and considerate. You can enjoy a quiet and tasty meal every time you visit. Be aware not all items in the menu are always available (eg. Hash Browns), but nonetheless, excellent!
Seems weird reviewing a McDonalds but this might be the best one in the lower mainland, spotless and the staff are friendly

Thank you to the kind Manager Mark who was working yesterday Tuesday Jan 15th 2019. I had taken a major fall in the parking lot, and was quite banged up. He was thoughtful and kind. The way he spoke to the staff and the customers was impressive and entertaining
Mobile order, enjoy your Jr. chicken while watching   &   land, what more could you want?
Service was great. They forgot to add the nugget meal to my order. But after going through the drive thru for the second time they made it right and gave me a apple pie
Good Mcdonalds! Quick and Get the order right! Which is very rare nowadays
We had muffins and coffee.  Both are good.  If you use your app to order, you might get discounts.
This is a well managed location. Clean, and not too busy. A good place for a quiet meal.

It ia one of a few McDonalds that has a theme. And they are hardly misplace the order. Foods are expected to be your usual McDonalds. The theme of this McDonalds is Aviation. It has lots of drawings, pictures about it. The place is facing YVR airport and has drive through. The staffs are friendly and they never miss a piece of cheese in your burger. That is a plus because some others they always miss something like straw, sauce.... when u are ordering drivethru
Quick, fast and efficient.  Was in and out and back on the road within 5 min
Pretty busy   as any one, but it make a difference when the employees are awesome         bathroom clean, food delicious
You like hambagubger like my daughter says? Then try here. But don t melt down of it comes apart while you dig in. She did that.
Service is always very good here, and love the location. Also come here in the summers on Thursday nights as theres an awesome gathering of classic cars.
Its fast food, the food is aways the same. McDonald is always delicious. But plus for this place for keeping it super clean and well lit!
good food
Very nice location, no mistakes, no errors. Very quick service everytime I visit here.
5 star soley for service. The food is consistent to other McDonalds but the staff that helped me at the drive thru window was extremely courteous and helpful.
This location is very convenient for those travelling from West Richmond into Vancouver, with the bonus of being a great place to watch planes take off at YVR.
100 will go back here! More fun and staffs are beautiful

Fast and well made food .. all McDonalds should be like this one. Also there is one very friendly manager that works there I am not sure what his name is but his attitude is awesome . Definitely one of my go to mcdonalds
Great McDonald s staff is super friendly and breakfast burritos are nice and full!
Quick and convenient.  Nice view if watching planes and helicopters in front of you if you park here
Great McDs..   polite, and friendly and consistent good food.  Love to sit outside and eat in the summer and watch the planes go by.
Super clean and efficient
Nice place to drop by with a friend for coffee and a muffin.  Staff pleasant and great location Thanks.
Best Mc Ds near the airport. DT on sundays is slower, DT guy needs a raise, just Mr Cool you know.
It s a good place do go. They offer dine in but no drink refills.
Not bad, the milk shake machine works 9/10 times. Youre welcome :)
Watching the planes take off and land during a late summer sunset while enjoying an ice cream is a treat into itself.
Great location, excellent service, and seems to taste better than other McDonalds.
The staff here are not great, but the manager of the store itself is great and believes in customer service. Ben is a great example of how a store manager should be!
Right by YVR. Great location for eats and planespotting. Clean with friendly service.
Very nice view to the airport  especially landing. Not to much people stays there like other McDonalds.
The food here was actually super fresh and tasty .
Good place to eat and chill, hope they bring refills back soon!
Fast and friendly service
Always fast with my drive-thru orders. Extremely professional :)
This is my favorite McDonalds because theres a nice view of the airport and planes fly right above you
Sometimes a bit slow but as a regular they treat us at MTU awesome!
Fast pace restaurent with a lovely weekly discount app. A great snack place when passing by.
Great staff. Bonus: Thursday evenings in the summer, car collectors gather to show off and talk about their cars.
Fast and friendly service at this McDonald s location  , loved their plain sundae
love this location, you can watch airplanes while you eat
This time they did not miss anything from our order. Great improvement.
Has some very enthusiastic staff working at the drive-thru! 10/10 would drive again!!!
Super fast drive thru service. Fastest Ive seen at McD
Close to the vancouver international airport.  If u like to see the airplanes, it is a definite recommand must go place.
Wow, the cashier very helpful and good customer service KS# 2
McDonalds in an isolated location. Good place to take a pit stop for those who like to cruise around the city.
Nice place to grab something and eat outside, looking the view... very calm place
I love the amazing view after ordering here
Always a vrrat meal and excellent service
Beautiful !
This is my favorite McDs of all.  Really fun staff and its properly prepared.
Used mobile app to place my order and picked it up at curbside. Worked great.
Theyre consistent.
Like this location.  Can see plane going up and down
I eat here yum yum yum
Staff very friendly and the food taste the same as usual
Good clean place. Good for coffee and a quick bite.
I mean cmon. Its McDonalds. Amazing fast food and it was pretty fast.
Nice location good customer service
Lovely place and workers are happy!
I asked for 4 mcdoubles and they forgot to charge me! Awesome
Always nice to eat fast at an airport!
First time there..awesome service
I have to admit that I was wrong about McDonalds. Part of a big family
Renovated. New and cozy. Nice airport view.
Better than on no2 mcdonald...
A good place to have breakfast during morning traffic.
Its Chez Rons...... What more to say?!?! Solid fast food!
Awesome view of the Vancouver International Airport runways.
Staff are super friendly and the food  was great!
Good place to watch jets take off, and sunset.
Prompt service, drive thru quick and efficient
McDs is always great! Always a big fan!
Great food with reasonable price..
